电影《[[雨人|雨人]]》的原型，患有[[學者症候群|學者症候群]]的[[金·匹克|金·匹克]]也患有胼胝体伴周围神经发育不全。

===性别差异===
在过去一百年里许多学者和爱好者研究和讨论胼胝体的性别差异。20世纪初的研究说男子与女子的胼胝体大小不同。这个结果受到质疑。后来更加高明的图像技术似乎反驳早先的性别差异。但是1990年的的先进计算机神经解剖学分析技术证明胼胝体的性别差异是明显的，但是仅仅局限于一定的部位，而且它们与一定测试的认知能力有联系<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1093/cercor/8.7.635|pmid=9823484|title=Sex differences in anatomic measures of interhemispheric connectivity: Correlations with cognition in women but not men|journal=Cerebral Cortex|volume=8|issue=7|pages=635–40|year=1998|last1=Davatzikos|first1=C|last2=Resnick|first2=S. M.}}</ref>。最近的磁共振成像技术发现，如果用科學方法將男女大腦的大小調整至一致後，女子的胼胝体正中矢状截面平均比较大<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1093/cercor/bhs253|pmid=22891036|title=Sexual Dimorphism in the Human Corpus Callosum: An MRI Study Using the OASIS Brain Database|journal=Cerebral Cortex|volume=23|issue=10|pages=2514–20|year=2012|last1=Ardekani|first1=B. A.|last2=Figarsky|first2=K.|last3=Sidtis|first3=J. J.}}</ref>。

近年来考察人的思想的形式和功能的方法不断提高和扩大。比如除传统的磁共振成像技术外[[功能性磁共振成像|功能性磁共振成像]]也被用来分析生理，这样可以研究分子渗入或者渗出一个特殊区域或者组织的速度、渗透的[[各向异性|各向异性]]和新陈代谢的速度。这些数据与人胼胝体的结构和微结构的性别差异数据一致<ref name="pmid14527611">{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/S1053-8119(03)00313-6 |title=Characterization of sexual dimorphism in the human corpus callosum |year=2003 |last1=Dubb |first1=Abraham |last2=Gur |first2=Ruben |last3=Avants |first3=Brian |last4=Gee |first4=James |journal=NeuroImage |volume=20 |pages=512–9 |pmid=14527611 |issue=1}}</ref><ref name="pmid15511657">{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/j.cogbrainres.2004.07.002 |title=Effects of handedness and gender on macro- and microstructure of the corpus callosum and its subregions: A combined high-resolution and diffusion-tensor MRI study |year=2004 |last1=Westerhausen |first1=René |last2=Kreuder |first2=Frank |last3=Sequeira |first3=Sarah Dos Santos |last4=Walter |first4=Christof |last5=Woerner |first5=Wolfgang |last6=Wittling |first6=Ralf Arne |last7=Schweiger |first7=Elisabeth |last8=Wittling |first8=Werner |journal=Cognitive Brain Research |volume=21 |issue=3 |pages=418–26 |pmid=15511657}}</ref><ref name="pmid15891572">{{cite journal |doi=10.1097/00001756-200505310-00003 |title=Sex differences in the human corpus callosum: Diffusion tensor imaging study |year=2005 |last1=Shin |first1=Yong-Wook |last2=Jin Kim |first2=Dae |last3=Hyon Ha |first3=Tae |last4=Park |first4=Hae-Jeong |last5=Moon |first5=Won-Jin |last6=Chul Chung |first6=Eun |last7=Min Lee |first7=Jong |last8=Young Kim |first8=In |last9=Kim |first9=Sun I. |last10=Kwon |first10=J. S. |journal=NeuroReport |volume=16 |issue=8 |pages=795–8 |pmid=15891572|display-authors=9 }}</ref>。

磁共振成像也被用来做特殊的三维数学关系分析，其结果发现与性别之间差别的数据一致<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/j.artmed.2009.05.007 |title=Morphometric analysis of brain images with reduced number of statistical tests: A study on the gender-related differentiation of the corpus callosum |year=2009 |last1=Kontos |first1=Despina |last2=Megalooikonomou |first2=Vasileios |last3=Gee |first3=James C. |journal=Artificial Intelligence in Medicine |volume=47 |pages=75–86 |pmid=19559582 |issue=1 |pmc=2732126}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.2298/VSP0611933S |title=Sexual dimorphism of the human corpus callosum: Digital morphometric study |year=2006 |last1=Spasojevic |first1=Goran |last2=Stojanovic |first2=Zlatan |last3=Suscevic |first3=Dusan |last4=Malobabic |first4=Slobodan |journal=Vojnosanitetski pregled |volume=63 |issue=11 |pages=933}}</ref>。在一篇回顾里特殊算法发现70%重要的性别差别<ref name ="gid">{{cite journal |doi=10.1109/IEMBS.2005.1617119 |chapter=Callosal Shapes at the Midsagittal Plane: MRI Differences of Normal Males, Normal Females, and GID |title=2005 IEEE Engineering in Medicine and Biology 27th Annual Conference |year=2005 |last1=Yokota |first1=Y. |last2=Kawamura |first2=Y. |last3=Kameya |first3=Y. |isbn=0-7803-8741-4 |pages=3055–8}}</ref>。

==其它联系==
有报道说音乐家较非音乐家的胼胝体前部较大<ref name="Levitin">Levitin, Daniel J. "This is Your Brain on Music", '</ref>。另外左手或者[[两手同利|两手同利]]的人的胼胝体比右手的人的胼胝体大0.75平方厘米，或者11%<ref name="Wit" /><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Driesen |first1=Naomi R. |first2=Naftali |last2=Raz |year=1995 |title=The influence of sex, age, and handedness on corpus callosum morphology: A meta-analysis |journal=Psychobiology |volume=23 |issue=3 |pages=240–7}}</ref>。这些区别集中在胼胝体的前部和后部，压部则没有区别<ref name="Wit">{{cite journal |doi=10.1126/science.4023705 |title=The brain connection: The corpus callosum is larger in left-handers |year=1985 |last1=Witelson |first1=S. |journal=Science |volume=229 |issue=4714 |pages=665–8 |pmid=4023705|bibcode = 1985Sci...229..665W }}</ref>。其它研究显示胼胝体的大小与语言记忆能力和语义编码测试结果有关<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/j.ijpsycho.2012.07.092 |title=Functional role of corpus callosum regions in human memory functioning |year=2012 |last1=Kozlovskiy |first1=S.A. |last2=Vartanov |first2=A.V. |last3=Pyasik |first3=M.M. |last4=Nikonova |first4=E.Y. |journal=International Journal of Psychophysiology |volume=85 |issue=3 |pages=396–7}}</ref>。患有[[失讀症|失讀症]]的孩子的胼胝体比较小和发育比较弱<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1001/archneur.1995.00540250036010 |title=Dyslexia and Corpus Callosum Morphology |year=1995 |last1=Hynd |first1=G. W. |last2=Hall |first2=J. |last3=Novey |first3=E. S. |last4=Eliopulos |first4=D. |last5=Black |first5=K. |last6=Gonzalez |first6=J. J. |last7=Edmonds |first7=J. E. |last8=Riccio |first8=C. |last9=Cohen |first9=M. |journal=Archives of Neurology |volume=52 |pages=32–8 |pmid=7826273 |issue=1 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/S0028-3932(01)00143-9 |title=Less developed corpus callosum in dyslexic subjects—a structural MRI study |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_neuropsychologia_2002_40_7/page/1035 |year=2002 |last1=Von Plessen |first1=K |journal=Neuropsychologia |volume=40 |issue=7 |pages=1035–44 |pmid=11900755 |last2=Lundervold |first2=A |last3=Duta |first3=N |last4=Heiervang |first4=E |last5=Klauschen |first5=F |last6=Smievoll |first6=AI |last7=Ersland |first7=L |last8=Hugdahl |first8=K}}</ref>。

在一段发育重要的时期音乐训练会提高胼胝体的体积。这说明左右手的调谐提高、白质的结构变化和运动和听觉的体积提高，帮助未来的音乐训练。研究发现6岁前就开始音乐训练的孩子（至少获得15个月的训练）的胼胝体体积提高，在11岁以前获得音乐训练的成年人的双手调节提高<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1523/JNEUROSCI.3578-12.2013|pmid=23325263|title=Early Musical Training and White-Matter Plasticity in the Corpus Callosum: Evidence for a Sensitive Period|journal=Journal of Neuroscience|volume=33|issue=3|pages=1282–90|year=2013|last1=Steele|first1=C. J.|last2=Bailey|first2=J. A.|last3=Zatorre|first3=R. J.|last4=Penhune|first4=V. B.}}</ref>。

==临床重要性==
===癫痫===
[[File:EEG_cap.jpg|thumb]]
[[胼胝体切开|胼胝体切开]]可以用来减轻[[癫痫|癫痫]]的症状<ref name="pmid17521926">{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/j.seizure.2007.04.004 |title=Corpus callosotomy: A palliative therapeutic technique may help identify resectable epileptogenic foci |year=2007 |last1=Clarke |first1=Dave F. |last2=Wheless |first2=James W. |last3=Chacon |first3=Monica M. |last4=Breier |first4=Joshua |last5=Koenig |first5=Mary-Kay |last6=McManis |first6=Mark |last7=Castillo |first7=Edward |last8=Baumgartner |first8=James E. |journal=Seizure |volume=16 |issue=6 |pages=545–53 |pmid=17521926}}</ref>。一般在大脑一侧发生发作或者[[强直－阵挛性发作|强直－阵挛性发作]]导致两个半脑之间电流的情况下会采取这个措施。在做手术前神经学家、神经外科医生、心理学家和神经放射医生使用[[腦電圖|腦電圖]]、核磁共振成像、正电子发射计算机断层扫描等来考察手术的可能性<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.webmd.com/epilepsy/corpus-callosotomy|title=WebMd Corpus Callotomy|publisher=Web MD|accessdate=2016年5月4日|date=2010年7月18日|archive-date=2012年12月20日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121220011938/http://www.webmd.com/epilepsy/corpus-callosotomy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

